<plot>The tale of a young man's struggle to establish a racial identity. Blending elements of 60's agit-prop political theater with surreal storytelling, the film provides a glimpse into the mind of its protagonist during an intense psychological and emotional breakdown. As an elaborately constructed fantasy world clashes with a past that haunts him, he suffers through a downward spiral as he loses a grip on reality.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?395743</url></doc>
